  "detailed_description": "Do you want a multiplayer trivia game with next to no frills? Then you've found it! This is SimplyTrivia, here are the features:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOnline Trivia Database: The main source of trivia is OpenTDB. Feel free to submit questions there!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCustom Question Packs: Create, download, and use packs of questions as trivia sources! Includes an intuitive and easy to use built-in editor for creating question packs.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOnline Multiplayer: Play with up to 7 friends at once!",
